unctional space with this smart TV unit with a hidden dresser<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Hidden Dressing Table For Small Bedroom | Dressing Unit Design Ideas for Small Bedroom | DesignCafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/hOlSkiLEHnk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Kitchen With A Foldable Breakfast Counter And Hidden Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Indian families love to have their meals together. We make sure we gather around the dining table and enjoy our meals with friends and family. Be it our regular meals or festive feasts. But with compact urban apartments, having a separate dining area is not a luxury everyone can afford. So why not make your kitchen multifunctional? This foldable breakfast counter is perfect for small families to enjoy their meals together or entertain guests while cooking. It also comes with hidden storage where you can stack your kitchen essentials. Just put the table back once you&#8217;re done with your meals and your kitchen is clean and mess-free.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160149\/space-saving-option-for-small-families-with-foldable-breakfast-counter-in-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Space saving option for small families with a foldable breakfast counter in kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-22179\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160149\/space-saving-option-for-small-families-with-foldable-breakfast-counter-in-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160149\/space-saving-option-for-small-families-with-foldable-breakfast-counter-in-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160149\/space-saving-option-for-small-families-with-foldable-breakfast-counter-in-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160149\/space-saving-option-for-small-families-with-foldable-breakfast-counter-in-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A foldable breakfast counter is a perfect space-saving option for small families<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Classy And Space-Saving Bar Unit Beneath The Staircase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With the recent pandemic, partying outside, pub hopping on weekends had become a distant dream. So why not turn a corner of your home into a cozy bar where you can chill with your friends or unwind in your pyjamas over a glass of wine? This bar unit utilizes the dead space under the staircase yet blends with the home&#8217;s design beautifully. The open bottle rack with sliding shutters, wine glass rack and drawers to store your bottle makes it an all in one unit. Just add two bar stools and your personalized bar is ready for a happening house party.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160107\/space-saving-bar-unit-under-staircase-for-small-families.jpg\" alt=\"Space saving bar unit under staircase for small families and apartments\" class=\"wp-image-22174\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160107\/space-saving-bar-unit-under-staircase-for-small-families.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160107\/space-saving-bar-unit-under-staircase-for-small-families-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160107\/space-saving-bar-unit-under-staircase-for-small-families-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160107\/space-saving-bar-unit-under-staircase-for-small-families-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An uber-cool bar unit for best utilisation of dead space beneath the staircase<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Cabinet In The Foyer Area With Drawers And Built-in Seating<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The foyer area if utilised intelligently can provide a lot of storage space in your home. A cabinet with deep pull out drawers helps you keep your shoes in an organised manner. You can also use some of the drawers to store your cushion covers, extra curtains and bedsheets. This cabinet comes with a pull out ottoman seating for you to sit and wear your shoes. You can space some nice decor elements on the top to add to the aesthetics of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160129\/space-saving-cabinet-with-inbuilt-seating-for-foyer-area.jpg\" alt=\"Space-saving cabinet with inbuilt seating for your foyer area\" class=\"wp-image-22176\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160129\/space-saving-cabinet-with-inbuilt-seating-for-foyer-area.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160129\/space-saving-cabinet-with-inbuilt-seati