-vanity-unit-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A space-saving bathroom design that accommodates your washing machine as well<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Pull Out Study Table Attached To Your Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With work from home being the new normal, a dedicated <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/home-office-design\/\">home office setup<\/a> has become the need of the hour. But if your home doesn&#8217;t have enough space to accommodate a separate workstation, this cosy little pull-out study table attached to the wardrobe will help you create a work environment for yourself where you can concentrate fully. It is space-saving, unique and stylish. Just get a comfortable chair for yourself and you are good to go. So stop yourself from working from your bed and get ready to take your work calls from your uber-cool home office.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160155\/space-saving-wardrobe-with-pull-out-study-table-for-small-families.jpg\" alt=\"Space saving wardrobe design with a pull out study table for small families\" class=\"wp-image-22180\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160155\/space-saving-wardrobe-with-pull-out-study-table-for-small-families.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160155\/space-saving-wardrobe-with-pull-out-study-table-for-small-families-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160155\/space-saving-wardrobe-with-pull-out-study-table-for-small-families-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/25160155\/space-saving-wardrobe-with-pull-out-study-table-for-small-families-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A comforta